=Description=
    
* Created by Tom Lowenhaupt (TomL@communisphere.com) - from a project to provide NYC's community board members, staffs, and residents witha range of governance communication services
    
* A wiki derived from the premise that city assigned "community boards" in New York were ineffective due to imistations in budgets and technology.
    
* The beyond voting wiki provides a means for community members to create a better system that identifies
    
* the goal is to create an improved governance structure for NYC
    
* The wiki allows users to give input on issues regarding institutional changesuch as:
          
o Lower Chamber
          
o Decentralization
          
o School Participation
          
o Youth Participation
          
o Elections
          
o and also allows you to give additional suggestions
